    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《谍：惊蛰》是一款谍战文字冒险游戏，改编自人民文学奖得主海飞的同名小说《惊蛰》，曾获中国台北国际电玩展最佳剧情游戏提名，腾讯游戏创作大赛银奖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏有40万余字不重复文本和4个不同结局，预计单周目游戏时长为10-15小时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是一款简单的视觉小说，你将在这里—— </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用城市地图，穿梭在重庆与上海，重现故事场景；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在故纸堆里捕捉历史的回声，见证风起云涌的谍海漩涡； </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入错综复杂的人物关系，影响每一位当局者的命运。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374000/extras/abcd8b933ef29c7f4406d6772bc7ad12.webp?t=1770349420\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374000/extras/8c45b8ae1fb1718dc730c3b3833020f2.poster.avif?t=1770349420\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374000/extras/8c45b8ae1fb1718dc730c3b3833020f2.webm?t=1770349420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一边是风雨飘摇的上海，一边是炮火四溅的重庆。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事将在这两座孤城中交替错落展开，带你深入同样时代背景下、有着不同风情和态势的情报战场。其地域跨度之大，叙事冲突之激烈，足以让你感受到冰火两重天般的极致体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374000/extras/0e719044011739bcbfb28777b6ed0d92.webp?t=1770349420\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374000/extras/5e388af1da99057d99d0afbae7f79b3a.poster.avif?t=1770349420\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374000/extras/5e388af1da99057d99d0afbae7f79b3a.webm?t=1770349420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >浑浑噩噩的“包打听”，被特务挟持的盲眼少女，潜伏在军统的中共卧底，性格泼辣的外科医生……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透过他们的视角，你将在推理解谜、做出抉择的过程中，逐渐拼凑起这场谍战风云的全貌。在游戏中，你需要帮助他们解除重重危机，在人性沉浮的谍海中共同进退。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374000/extras/1234e66c0cd68299ed9cf1909b8778bd.webp?t=1770349420\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374000/extras/f9f3153200bbe61f428ee8c907d15c5b.poster.avif?t=1770349420\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374000/extras/f9f3153200bbe61f428ee8c907d15c5b.webm?t=1770349420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实地拍摄的场景、真实可考的《大公报》、早已绝版的影印书……只为还原你不知道的一九四〇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在牵一发动全身的蝴蝶效应下，每一处线索、每一份情报都有可能改变当局者的命运。游戏内置多个分支和结局，以及高达50条死亡分线，即便N刷也能带来不一样的游戏体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2374000/extras/9ebaf289047a3ca4ce63362ee3f6cc17.webp?t=1770349420\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好乐猫工作室，一群做游戏的。17年不幸入坑，至今仍在苟活，成员来来走走，目前还剩5个。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坚信办法总比困难多，奈何梦比游戏做得好。幸而残余同伙个个不聪明，多少有点一根筋，打算在做不动之前都一直做下去。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作人常说，昼短苦夜长，何不秉烛游？嘛钱不钱的，乐呵乐呵得了。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（声明：本作中不含任何AI绘画、AI文字等辅助生成内容。本游戏基于真实历史背景衍生而来，但不涉及现实事件改编内容。游戏中包含的人名、地名、物品名及故事情节纯属虚构，不与现实世界产生对应联系，如有雷同，纯属巧合。）</p>",
